WEBVTT

00:00:08.954 --> 00:00:11.079
"Sorry, my phone died."

00:00:11.121 --> 00:00:13.079
"It's nothing. I'm fine."

00:00:13.663 --> 00:00:16.579
"These allegations
are completely unfounded."

00:00:17.038 --> 00:00:20.454
"The company was not aware
of any wrongdoing."

00:00:21.121 --> 00:00:22.704
"I love you."

00:00:23.704 --> 00:00:27.038
We hear anywhere
from 10 to 200 lies a day,

00:00:27.079 --> 00:00:30.371
and we spent much of our history
coming up with ways to detect them,